title: Reza Habibzadeh
text: Reza Habibzadeh (, born April 13, 1996 in <a href="Tehran">Tehran</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>) is an Iranian <a href="soccer">football</a> <a href="Midfielder%20%28association%20football%29">midfielder</a> who currently plays for <a href="Paykan%20F.C.">Paykan</a> in the <a href="Persian%20Gulf%20Pro%20League">Persian Gulf Pro League</a>.
